Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.03,0:02:15.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,願望之星 想念之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.99,0:02:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的飯還真是好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.32,0:02:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不對啊 秋菜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.81,0:02:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.73,0:02:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不就跟平常一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉唷 秋菜大人您真謙虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.67,0:02:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直就是高尚的女孩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海朵拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.31,0:02:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.43,0:02:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用餐的時候請安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣有失禮節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是麻煩耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.44,0:03:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.61,0:03:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒通知一聲就住在我家 已經三天了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.53,0:03:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.62,0:03:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.64,0:03:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將帶有兩個電子的鋰加入兩個1s
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,融合的時候再加入一個電子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,法姆老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.98,0:03:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋰的電子應該是三個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊  對…對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要一直跟著我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.11,0:04:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.07,0:04:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為近期將要舉行送星之宴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.37,0:04:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想讓秋菜小姐擔任這次儀式的巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送星之宴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.01,0:04:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史雷普尼爾大彗星的接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.01,0:04:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該在瓦爾哈拉的週期是比較早的不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.71,0:04:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ㄧ個月後就會在地球附近通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.49,0:04:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來 地球和瓦爾哈拉星在銀河系是相對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.32,0:04:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,替史雷普尼爾大彗星送行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這個儀式裡 由亞（指美麗的女性）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.72,0:04:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是在地球稱為巫女的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.21,0:04:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將三張寫在短籤上的願望奉納
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.71,0:04:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至於巫女一職 秋菜小姐才是適合的人選
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.71,0:04:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們之前就是秘密地觀察著秋菜小姐的人品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都不秘密好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.36,0:05:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 賞月耶 好期待唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.64,0:05:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問 這樣子的話 我也必須要出席嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.07,0:05:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,負責把三個願望寫在短籤上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是巫女本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.78,0:05:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瓦爾哈啦家的領導人 以及王家女婿三人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.06,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼都還沒答應啊‥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.99,0:05:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能擔任送星之宴的巫女是非常榮譽的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.08,0:05:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的意思是除了秋菜小姐別無其他人選
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.16,0:05:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秋秋秋…秋菜小姐 她太過興奮了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就就就…就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.44,0:05:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點說妳要做 啊不 請快說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.18,0:05:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.77,0:05:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我們今天就來準備一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.75,0:06:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.78,0:06:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先 衣服為和式的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 秋菜好漂亮唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.18,0:06:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以說是惹人憐愛哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的眼光果然沒錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.33,0:06:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.33,0:06:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家說得太誇張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 一點都不誇張喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的啊 很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.95,0:06:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在儀式舉行之前 必須徹底的演練一番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.21,0:07:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓秋菜小姐完美地學會奉納的舞蹈和規定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.47,0:07:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.98,0:07:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.32,0:07:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.83,0:07:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和人 我們去買東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.99,0:07:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天二町目的超市有特賣會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.61,0:07:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等等要排練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,練排?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.30,0:07:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,排練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.69,0:07:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啦 我們去特賣會嘛 走嘛走嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呵呵 對不起喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.77,0:07:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 瓦爾古蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.25,0:07:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.45,0:07:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和人最近都不陪我玩 好無聊唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.49,0:08:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.90,0:08:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瓦爾也好想當巫女喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.07,0:08:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個不錯唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.97,0:08:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說不定很適合穿巫女裝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是尺寸會不合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.02,0:08:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉  哥哥只要一不在 這裡的工作就多到不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.38,0:08:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.26,0:08:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為出席儀式是王家女婿的義務呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過秋菜好漂亮唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瓦爾哈啦所選中的巫女 秋菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.97,0:08:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可謂是宇宙第一的巫女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.66,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是在冥王星軌道上建造中的神殿衛星的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確認完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.21,0:09:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送星之宴將在這個神殿衛星上舉行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.76,0:09:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在建造的完成度為62%　
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能會比建造公司的預定時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍微慢一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.57,0:09:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕的上儀式時間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.43,0:09:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管如何 一定要讓它來得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.28,0:09:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不說這個 涅斯緹 妳那邊如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.83,0:09:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海賊掃蕩任務碰到些小麻煩 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來還需要一點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.49,0:09:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依照慣例 送星之宴中八大皇女全員都必須出席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.72,0:09:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不容許遲到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.49,0:09:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.30,0:09:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶～贏了贏了 積木倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.72,0:10:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.97,0:10:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.10,0:10:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也要來我家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.18,0:10:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.61,0:10:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總不能偷懶不練習啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.88,0:10:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真辛苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.32,0:10:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.07,0:10:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.68,0:10:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都在練舞不是很辛苦嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.41,0:10:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.09,0:10:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 好像總是把你捲進奇怪的事情中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪會 沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也算是巫女的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.41,0:11:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女婿大人 今天也請你多多指教囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也請你多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.91,0:11:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巫女大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我先回去做準備囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.47,0:11:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的舞步越來越融入感情了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.53,0:11:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不愧是地球的巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神殿衛星沒有意外地竣工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.07,0:12:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在 全員往冥王星出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都到齊了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.46,0:12:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.24,0:12:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題吧 大家都在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.32,0:12:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…說起來總覺得好像有人不在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這邊的都來了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瓦爾在唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瓦爾哈啦王家這邊的人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.89,0:12:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,涅斯緹姐姐晚點才會到不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.55,0:12:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萊娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.86,0:12:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可菈斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萊娜在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.60,0:13:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道耶 我最近也是覺得老見不到她人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萊娜 萊娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到請回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.45,0:13:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 至少 通訊器應該不在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.13,0:13:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定又是在宇宙某處溜達了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.24,0:13:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是給我找到萊娜 一定要好好的給她個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.15,0:13:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是八大皇女沒到齊的話 就會糟蹋了送星之宴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.00,0:13:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.12,0:13:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史雷普尼爾大彗星都已經這麼接近了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又來玩囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萊娜…她在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.09,0:13:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然說還小但也不能說沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但都要舉行儀式了 就饒了她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.41,0:14:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說 我現在是被強行帶走的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,願望嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.07,0:14:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.15,0:14:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王家的領導者 女婿 以及巫女三人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.81,0:14:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在短籤上各自寫下願望 再進行獻納
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是什麼願望都行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.66,0:14:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 但是 絕對不能讓別人看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.69,0:14:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,短籤要倒蓋著然後放流到宇宙中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.39,0:14:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 希望你們能先想好當天要寫什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.62,0:14:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瓦爾也不能寫願望嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.97,0:14:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 聽說不是被決定的人就不能寫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.00,0:14:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 小瓦爾的願望 就給和人來寫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.65,0:14:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瓦爾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.89,0:14:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想跟大家一起去宇宙旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不就是了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 和人有什麼願望呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.91,0:15:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我說 告訴其他人是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.19,0:15:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對嘛 不行唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,願望...啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.56,0:15:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.36,0:15:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.25,0:15:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 不僅壯觀 還好大耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.23,0:16:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經接近預定時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.47,0:16:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 請盡快做好準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.75,0:16:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.13,0:16:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我們等到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇～成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.31,0:16:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒開始嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.83,0:17:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是因為涅斯緹大人遲遲還沒出現的原因…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,涅斯緹還沒到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 仍然無法取得連絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果 涅斯緹來不及的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現不明飛行物體急速接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.04,0:17:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.08,0:17:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.63,0:17:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎擊準備呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來不及完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.78,0:17:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個煙火是妳放的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.40,0:18:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代替禮物的新花樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當作是送星儀式的應景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.55,0:20:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛走了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.85,0:20:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真美呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儀式辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.12,0:20:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在 我覺得有種充實的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.16,0:20:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以瓦爾哈拉家族的身分完成了這個儀式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.00,0:21:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從今以後也必須要加油呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.16,0:21:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了我們的將來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.93,0:21:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.56,0:21:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡 這裡唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.67,0:21:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉唷 等一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.40,0:21:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.11,0:21:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.26,0:21:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望瓦爾哈拉國運長久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是梅穆姊姊的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.09,0:21:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望時乃湯生意興隆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.93,0:21:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是哥哥的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.89,0:21:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.08,0:21:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,短籤上寫的東西是不能看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.32,0:22:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是連帶責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.57,0:22:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接?受?處?罰?吧!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.59,0:22:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是實現了該有多好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.20,0:22:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的願望

